{
  "texts": [
    "We make isolated changes to the information set.",
    "In particular, we have different initial data conditions.",
    "In the \"no data\" condition, the experiment begins with five unknown mountains, while in the other conditions, it begins with one mountain revealed as either high, low or, medium value.",
    "Note: This table illustrates how we specify the key parameters of GABE to replicate the online lab experiment of Hoelzemann et al. (2024).",
    "See the text and Appendix A.1 for more details."
  ]
}